attributes.Long form description: The student's task begins with him assembling the base of the rolling cart which consists of screwing the side bars and assembling the base frames and then mounting the side bars on the base frames, after this he assembles each of the trays by sliding them into the side bars and fixing them using the brackets, finally after assembling the trays the student assembles the wheels by screwing them to the base of the rolling cart.
